{"tid":1927621,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"We lost a hero 14/3 Battle of Hong Kong Veteran","createTime":"2020-03-16T01:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T15:58:26.000Z","uid":238660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14dd92a745341d908b4c33c3ab13c4d6465d9fda","tid":1927621,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:27:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ErinOTooleMP/status/1238946285408997377?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FErinOTooleMP%2Fstatus%2F1238946285408997377%3Fs%3D19&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvpLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=576d635f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FErinOTooleMP%2Fstatus%2F1238946285408997377%3Fs%3D19&h=01bdbbfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ErinOTooleMP/status/1238946285408997377?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人，我哋喺3月14號失去另一位最老嘅手足，失去一位保護香港嘅英雄，佢保衞香港嗰陣我哋未出世。<br />\n<br />\nCanada lost a hero yesterday (14/3)with the passing of Ralph McLean. Battle of Hong Kong Veteran<br />\n<br />\n佢為香港打過一場九死一生嘅血戰，再坐三年零八個月集中營，要知道盟軍喺香港好慘烈，冇增援冇退路仲要係喺東亞捱日軍。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;We were supposed to set up a defence against the Japanese. We could see nothing. We had no idea where we were. And in the morning, at daybreak, we were attacked from behind.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n#香港保衛戰"},{"pid":"f5b915a11f1edce1c38e2149aada38b74d400b0f","tid":1927621,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:29:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd0f7bf0a446508a8dbf0c676cc4a734ed7cdce1","tid":1927621,"uid":322010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45a28e72e131cf13bbdfb7f821c63c116f150e47","tid":1927621,"uid":238660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T01:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/